    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the meatballs are cooking, bash the <strong>spices</strong> into a fine powder in the <strong>pestle & mortar</strong></p><p>Add most of the<strong> ground turmeric </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your <strong>Kashmiri-style spice blend</strong></p>",
