    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>tomatoes</strong> into wedges</p><p>Once the meatballs have browned, add a generous knob of <strong>butter</strong> to the pan with the<strong> sliced onion</strong>, <strong>Kashmiri-style spice blend </strong>and<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>and cook for 5-6 min or until the onion has softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>tomato wedges </strong>and cook for 3-4 min further or until the meatballs are cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
