    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 2 min, mix the <strong>turmeric</strong> through the <strong>basmati rice </strong>– this is your <strong>turmeric stained rice</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>Kashmiri-style lamb meatball curry</strong> with the <strong>turmeric stained rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
